%% D-09 Meeting Join Flow — source: SPEC.md Appendix A
sequenceDiagram
  Client->>APIGateway: open meeting link
  APIGateway->>Identity: authenticate/guest
  APIGateway->>Authorisation: validate access
  APIGateway->>MeetingOrchestration: request join
  MeetingOrchestration->>MediaControl: choose region/provider
  MeetingOrchestration-->>Client: media token
  Client->>SFUProvider: establish media
